HEADWORD: Sulphuring
<hw>Sul"phur*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Exposure to the fumes of
burning sulphur, as in bleaching; the process of bleaching by exposure
to the fumes of sulphur.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sulphurize</ent>⟦br⟧
